Replica sets:
Make sure pod copies are running in cluster.
When pod is crashed, it replaces that pod with it's replica.
3 pods --> p1, p2, p3 --> 5  -->p*1, p*2, p*3, p, p.
P1 --> crashed: p*1 will replace p1.
It will manages pods.

	1. Selector: it decides which pod is managed by replicaset.
	2. Count of replica set.
	3. Pod template that defines how new pods should be created.

When to use:
	1. When u want ur pods to be managed.
	2. When u want to create replicas.

